                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="'The Purge' is a frightening sci-fi horror-triller, that leaves a massive impression! Its razor-sharp! Performance-Wise: Ethan Hawke stands out with a stellar performance. He's heroic all through. Lena Headey is marvelously restrained. Adelaide Kane is highly commendable. Max Burkholder is adequate. Rhys Wakefield is loathsome. On the whole, 'The Purge' is an experience.&#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

