                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/P4qVVL3/4-5-stars-2.png" WidthRequest="70"/>
                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="The concept of the purge is brilliant. Being a huge fan of dystopia, the idea is interesting and has so much potential to become something that people remember. As good as this film is, it doesn't quite give the concept justice. It was a good movie, except it could have been better.&#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

